        <ul>
          <li>Scripting using a Java like syntax.</li>
          <li>Merging of any number of docked structures.</li>
          <li>Direct download from the PDB.</li>
          <li>Trajectory playback.</li>
          <li>Selection</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Based on graphics picking</li>
            <li>Based on a hierarchical molecular tree</li>
          </ul>
          <li>Configurable Labels</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Atoms</li>
            <li>Residues</li>
          </ul>
          <li>Measurement</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Distances</li>
            <li>Angles</li>
            <li>Dihedrals</li>
          </ul>
          <li>Rotation and translation</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Of individual molecules</li>
            <li>Of the global frame</li>
          </ul>
          <li>Global Zooming.</li>
          <li>3D display methods</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Wireframe</li>
            <li>Spacefill</li>
            <li>Tube</li>
